### Constraints

```php
// Required field
Expect::string()->required()

// Nullable (accepts null)
Expect::string()->nullable()

// Default value
Expect::string()->default('hello')
Expect::string('hello')  // shorthand

// Length/count limits
Expect::string()->min(3)->max(100)
Expect::array()->min(1)->max(10)

// Numeric range
